# CV ingest (diagnosis)

## Read first

- [ADR-001 § CV policy](../../docs/decisions/ADR-001-adaptive-diagnosis-ctrr.md)
- [CV-PARSING backlog](../../docs/backlog/CV-PARSING.md)

## MVP scope

- **PDF only** (`application/pdf`)
- Text extract via library — **no LLM in extract step**
- Optional one-shot LLM → `CvSignals` (skills, roles, years_hint)
- Fail open: missing/invalid CV → diagnosis continues from intake + interview

## Anti-patterns

- ❌ Require CV to start diagnosis
- ❌ LinkedIn scrape in hackathon MVP
- ❌ Store raw PDF in sessionStorage for production (move to backend on start)

## Linear

HAC-33 (epic) · blocks enriched skip logic in HAC-43
